Package dog.giraffe.points

Interface Sum

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Sum.SingleVariable
    public interface Sum
    Instances of Sum represents the sum of a mutable list of double values. As this is a reference type, instances can be used in generic containers, and they are mutable unlike Doubles. The default implementation only stores a single running sum, trading numerical stability for speed.
